      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 1 <span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">poin </span><span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">Hydro DMG</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/1023623/1ce09211f025bf5470682189e0837732_5059381128712329062.png",
                "id": "talent70546",
                "key": "Water Ball",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Water Ball"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 3 poin<span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>.<span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\"> </span>Karakter target menerima<span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Refraction</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">.</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Refraction</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Saat Karakter terpengaruh bertukar ke Karakter lain:</span> perlu mengahabiskan 1 Dadu Elemental lebih banyak.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Durasi (Ronde): 2</span></p><p>(Maksimum satu status di sisi yang sama)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/1023623/2b72995c4a7d257472864199056edd68_7722316775463817208.png",
                "id": "talent20931",
                "key": "Influx Blast",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Influx Blast"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 5 <span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">poin </span><span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">Hydro DMG</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/1023623/57d2f05c0e87c6021cd6e4bfb5b031c1_6535957427677773335.png",
                "id": "talent77678",
                "key": "Rippled Reflection",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Rippled Reflection"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Memberikan Hydro dan memicu Reaksi Elemental berikut:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Vaporize</span>: DMG +2 poin untuk kasus ini</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, mengakibatkan 1 Piercing DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Frozen</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, target tidak dapat melangkah di Ronde ini (Dapat dihapus di muka setelah target menerima Physical DMG atau Pyro DMG, namun DMG +2)</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Bloom</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, menciptakan sebuah [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dendro Core</span>] yang memberikan +2 poin DMG untuk kasus Pyro/Electro DMG-mu selanjutnya</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/1023623/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_3657629840326304891.png",
                "id": "talent3057",
                "key": "Hydro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Hydro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Durasi (Ronde)</span></strong></p><p>Setiap kali kamu mencapai Tahap Selesai di setiap Ronde, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Durasi (Ronde)</span> -1.</p><p>Kartu ini akan langsung dibuang setelah <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Durasi (Ronde)</span> habis.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/03/04/25750596/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_3010109550798605873.png",
